myself back as much as I need.

00:37:18.120 --> 00:37:20.490
So I guess I find
most of the release--

00:37:20.490 --> 00:37:23.060
I feel more calm
when I'm writing,

00:37:23.060 --> 00:37:25.230
or I'm recording or playing.

00:37:25.230 --> 00:37:27.513
But the time-- unfortunately,
when you're on the road,

00:37:27.513 --> 00:37:30.180
