Talent" on Saturday.

00:43:22.903 --> 00:43:25.507
And all of a sudden, bang,
she wasn't even expecting it.

00:43:25.507 --> 00:43:27.590
Do you think you would
have coped with that at 18?

00:43:27.590 --> 00:43:28.492
KELLY JONES: No.

00:43:28.492 --> 00:43:29.200
I couldn't do it.

00:43:29.200 --> 00:43:30.825
I couldn't do live
tele every Saturday.

00:43:30.825 --> 00:43:31.750
I'd fall apart.

00:43:31.750 --> 00:43:32.297
No chance.

00:43:32.297 --> 00:43:33.630
GETHIN JONES: I can't do it now.

00:43:33.630 --> 00:43:34.320
KELLY JONES: No.

00:43:34.320 --> 00:43:36.028
I couldn't, honestly,
genuinely couldn't.

00:43:36.028 --> 00:43:39.100
I've never enjoyed one live
TV show my entire life.

00:43:39.100 --> 00:43:40.510
No.

00:43:40.510 --> 00:43:42.285
I mean, when it's
finished, I like it,

00:43:42.285 --> 00:43:44.640
